location.fullValue: The Ambler Plan, The Reserve at Cedar Point

data.description: Stunning and spacious custom brick ranch home with water views. Enjoy sunrises and sunsets from two rear decks. Tucked away in Cedar Point Golf Course community. This home is situated alongside a non-buildable protected wetland that provides a natural fence line for privacy. The home features a Generac 22KW whole house back-up generator, tankless water heater, Culligan water filtration system, dual zone heating and cooling, and Andersen windows and doors. The attic is walk-in and enormous with opportunities to create finished living spaces or expanded storage. The crawl space is encapsulated with a dehumidifier. This home is truly a unicorn. DO NOT pass on this unique opportunity
